  ('social-worker-moex-05830', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關「信度」的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["是指測量工具的穩定性", "將一個很準的體重器調低了2公斤，該體重器仍具有信度", "是指測量工具可以正確地測量出所欲測量之概念的程度", "可以透過在不同時間進行測量，藉由比較前後測量結果的相關程度來檢測之"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9f7d5685624f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b2e59b626294", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05831', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '型Ⅰ錯誤稱為α，型Ⅱ錯誤稱為β，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["在不增加α的情況下，我們可以增加樣本數達到降低β的目的", "1-β稱為檢定力，對立假設為真時，錯誤判斷的機率", "β是指虛無假設為假，不拒絕虛無假設的機率", "α是指虛無假設為真，但拒斥虛無假設的機率"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9f7d5685624f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b2e59b626294", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05832', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關固定樣本研究（panel study）的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["其成本低容易執行", "若執行得當，其研究結果具有很高的解釋力", "執行過程中可能會有樣本流失率過高的問題", "必須是相同母全體、相同的樣本，在不同的時間進行觀察"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9f7d5685624f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b2e59b626294", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05833', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一項科學的論點或見解，必須具備的特性為：', '["大膽假設，小心求證", "言之成理，符合事實", "溫暖的心，冷靜的腦", "見山不是山，見水不是水"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9f7d5685624f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b2e59b626294", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05834', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關抽樣誤差（sampling error）的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["抽樣誤差可分成處理誤差（processing error）與回應誤差（response error）", "抽樣誤差是樣本統計量的值與相對應的母體參數值間的差異", "一般來說，「機率抽樣法」較「非機率抽樣法」的抽樣誤差小", "一般來說，抽取的樣本數越多，抽樣誤差愈小"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9f7d5685624f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b2e59b626294", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05835', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關「信度」的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["我們可以「複本法（alternative forms method）」來檢查測量的等值性（equivalence）", "我們可以「重測法（test-retest method）」來檢查測量的穩定性（stability）", "我們可以「施測者間法（inter-rater method）」來檢查測量的充分性（sufficiency）", "我們可以「折半法（split-half method）」來檢查測量的內部一致性（internal consistency）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9f7d5685624f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b2e59b626294", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05836', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '某社工人員在撰寫有關課後照顧的評估報告時，參考了一篇由Chatili Das、Mary Ellen Kondrat、Ching Man Lam、Lee S. Shulman四位作者所共同撰寫的文章。依APA格式，在此評估報告的「參考文獻」中，這 篇文獻作者的寫法應該是：', '["C. Das, M. E. Kondrat, C. M. Lam, and L. S. Shulman", "Chatili Das, Mary Ellen Kondrat, Ching Man Lam, Lee S. Shulman", "Das, C., Kondrat, M. E., Lam, C. M., and Shulman, L. S", "Chatili, D., Mary, E. K., Ching, M. L., and Lee, S. S. 情況：假想廖教授計劃以臺灣社會工作專業人員協會的所有會員進行普查。研究者所擬定的其中一個研究假設 為「女性社工人員的倫理兩難決斷力較男性來得高」。請依上述資料回答下列第13題至第16題"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9f7d5685624f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b2e59b626294", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-05837', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '以上說明是屬於那一種研究假設？', '["問題型", "宣示型", "概念型", "虛無型"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9f7d5685624f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b2e59b626294", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105090", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次中醫師分階段營養師心理師護理師社工師暨法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
